---
description: Requirements authority and traceability for blueprint-driven work
globs:
alwaysApply: true
---

- Treat `blueprints/original/*.md` as read-only.
- Read the relevant blueprint sections before changing behavior.
- Document 10 overrides documents 01–09 only where explicit.
- Record accepted clarifications in `blueprints/amendments/` and `docs/DECISION_LOG.md`.
- Every implemented contract must map to schema, API/domain command, authorization, audit, tests and acceptance evidence.
- Never shorten scope by silently omitting blueprint behavior.
